VimSpeak
========

Introduction:
-------------

  interface to speak texts from vim using MSAgent.

Installation:
-------------

    # cd /path/to/your/vim/bundle
    # git clone https://github.com/mattn/vimspeak-vim

Usage:
------

    :'<,'>VimSpeak

  or

    :VimSpeak foo

